Formerly Route 672 "Storrs-Willimantic".
Three branches of this route exist:
674A: Serving the "Four Corners" area of Storrs and the Holiday Mall
674B: Express - Foster Drive to UConn East Campus.
674C: South Eagleville Road, Mansfield Senior Center, and the Mansfield Transportation Center .
